<br>
Some say if you drag a corpse in Velious you assume the faction of the corpse and Wuoshi will kill you.  Others say, nah, it is OK to drag the corpse.<br>
<br>
2 Guildmates went the other day and one tartgeted the corpse and the other targeted Wuoshi.  The one that tageted Wuoshi, got out of his sight until his con returned indiff and then assisted the guildie that had the corpse targeted and then summoned the corpse.  This works but if you can actually just walk up and drag it solo, it would make rescuing folks much easier.<br>
